The paper focuses on accelerating ConvNets, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and augmented reality (cs.AR) research. The use of FPGAs also falls under the categories of embedded systems (cs.ET) and systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the co-design of algorithms and hardware, which is relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) research.
